{{ja-kanjitab|ふう|yomi=o}}
{{IPAfont|/puː/}} → {{IPAfont|/fuː/}}

From {{bor|ja|ltc|sort=ふう|-}} {{ltc-l|風||id=1}}.

In {{w|Old Japanese}}, this kanji was used to transcribe the {{m|ja|借音|tr=shakuon}} ''kana'' of {{IPAfont|⟨pu⟩}} and {{IPAfont|⟨bu⟩}} in the ''{{w|Nihon Shoki}}'' (720 {{CE}}).

{{ja-noun|ふう}}

# a [[style]]
#: {{ja-usex|[[中国]]'''風'''|^ちゅうごく-'''ふう'''|China-'''style'''}}
#: {{ja-usex|[[そんな]]'''風'''に[[言う|言って]]くれて[[ありがとう]]。|そんな '''ふう''' に いってくれて ありがとう。|Thank you for telling me that.|lit=Thank you for telling me that in that '''way'''.}}

